T*
(rules. This means students must move beyond the overview and understand how the idea) Tj
T*
(actually works. A strong explanation should unpack the rules, relationships, or patterns) Tj
T*
(behind Probability and show how those ideas guide correct answers. In Mathematics,) Tj
T*
(success usually depends on understanding the symbols, rules, and steps that belong to) Tj
T*
(the topic.) Tj
