() Tj
T*
(3. How The Idea Is Applied) Tj
T*
(A useful way to teach Probability is to connect the explanation directly to finding the) Tj
T*
(probability of drawing a particular card or rolling a number. That kind of worked) Tj
T*
(calculation shows students how the topic moves from theory into use. At this stage, the) Tj
T*
(learner should be able to state the relevant rule or principle, explain why it fits the) Tj
T*
(question, and then apply the solution method with confidence.) Tj
